snippet.title: CyberSeas Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the CyberSeas! 
A post-apocalyptic near-future where cyber pirates rule the flooded remains of civilisation. 
Race around sunken streets in your jet-ship, swing between collapsed skyscrapers with your trusty harpoon, and build your reputation amongst its colourful inhabitants.

Featuring three unique levels to explore and dozens of missions to complete. 
CyberSeas is coming soon to Steam!

Music by Karl Casey @ White Bat Audio
